item.title: CVE-2021-33183|2024-09-17T03:33:59.466Z -- synology -- synology%20docker
item.description: Improper limitation of a pathname to a restricted directory ('Path Traversal') vulnerability container volume management component in Synology Docker before 18.09.0-0515 allows local users to read or write arbitrary files via unspecified vectors.
